Edie Martin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edie_Martin 0 Edie Martin (1 January 1880 – 22 February 1964) was a British actress. She was a ubiquitous performer, on stage from 1886, playing generally small parts but in high demand, appearing in scores of British films (although often uncredited). She appeared in several Ealing comedies. Edie_Martin ( 1_January_1880 – 22_February_1964 ) was a_British_actress .
